BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 85.44 600 Td (Chapter 1: Amazon Selling Overview) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Amazon is the largest online marketplace with over 300 million active customers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Third-party sellers account for nearly sixty percent of all Amazon sales.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (You do not need to manufacture products. You can resell existing items.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (There are multiple business models: retail arbitrage, wholesale, and private label.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Retail arbitrage means buying discounted items in stores and reselling on Amazon.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Wholesale means buying in bulk from manufacturers at reduced prices.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Private label means creating your own branded products manufactured for you.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Amazon handles shipping and customer service if you use their FBA program.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Average startup costs range from five hundred to three thousand dollars.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Many sellers earn their first sale within two to four weeks of starting.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (This is a real business that requires effort, patience, and learning.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (This book will walk you through every step from account setup to scaling.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (1) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
