BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 39.360000000000014 600 Td (Chapter 2: Individual vs Professional Accounts) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Amazon offers two seller account types: Individual and Professional.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Individual accounts are free monthly but charge 99 cents per item sold.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Professional accounts cost 39.99 per month but have no per-item fee.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (If you plan to sell more than 40 items per month, go Professional.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Professional accounts unlock advertising, bulk listing tools, and reports.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Individual accounts cannot win the Buy Box which is where most sales happen.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (You can start with Individual and upgrade to Professional at any time.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Both account types pay the same referral fees, usually 15 percent of price.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Professional sellers can create listings for products not yet on Amazon.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (You need a bank account, credit card, government ID, and tax information.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Amazon verifies your identity which can take a few days to complete.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Choose Professional from the start if you are serious about building a business.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (2) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
