BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 108.48 600 Td (Chapter 4: Sourcing Products) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Retail arbitrage is the fastest way to start: buy clearance items and resell.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Scan products using the Amazon Seller app to see selling price and fees instantly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Stores like Walmart, Target, and TJ Maxx have profitable clearance sections.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Look for items priced 75 percent or more below their Amazon selling price.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Wholesale sourcing means buying directly from brands at 50 percent off retail.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Find wholesale suppliers at trade shows, industry directories, and online.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Contact brands directly and ask for their wholesale program requirements.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Private label involves finding manufacturers on Alibaba to make your product.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (When using Alibaba, order samples from three to five suppliers before committing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Minimum order quantities for private label are usually 500 to 1000 units.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Always get product liability insurance when selling private label items.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Start with arbitrage to learn Amazon, then graduate to wholesale or private label.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (4) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
