q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Go to sellercentral.amazon.com and click the sign up button.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Have ready: government ID, bank statement, credit card, and phone number.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Amazon will verify your identity through a video call or document upload.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (The verification process typically takes two to five business days.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Once approved, complete your seller profile with your business information.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Set up your deposit method so Amazon can send you your sales revenue.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Configure your shipping settings and return address in account settings.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Explore Seller Central and familiarize yourself with the dashboard layout.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (The main sections are inventory, orders, advertising, and reports.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Enable two-factor authentication to protect your seller account.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Download the Amazon Seller app for managing your business on the go.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Your account is now ready for you to list your first product.) Tj ET
