BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 73.92000000000002 600 Td (Chapter 6: Listing Your First Product) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Search for your product on Amazon to see if a listing already exists.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (If the listing exists, click Sell on Amazon to add your offer to it.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (If no listing exists, create a new one with title, description, and images.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Choose the correct category and subcategory for your product type.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Fill in all product details: brand, size, color, material, and weight.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Set your selling price competitively based on research of similar items.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Determine your fulfillment method: FBA \(Amazon ships\) or FBM \(you ship\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (For FBA, set your quantity and create a shipping plan to send items in.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Indicate product condition accurately: new, used, refurbished, or collectible.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Add your SKU number to track inventory and identify products easily.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Review everything carefully before publishing. Accuracy builds trust.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Your listing will be active within minutes of publishing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (6) Tj ET

