BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 100.80000000000001 600 Td (Chapter 7: Product Photography) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Amazon requires the main image to have a pure white background.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (The product should fill at least 85 percent of the image frame.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Main images cannot include text, logos, watermarks, or props.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Use at least seven images: main, lifestyle, infographic, and detail shots.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Lifestyle images show your product being used by real people in context.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Infographic images highlight key features and dimensions with text overlays.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Detail shots show texture, craftsmanship, and quality up close.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Hire a photographer on Fiverr for 50-100 dollars if you cannot do it yourself.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Image dimensions should be at least 2000 pixels for the zoom feature.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Products with seven or more images convert significantly higher than those with fewer.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Compare your images to the best sellers in your category for quality standards.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Great images are your most important investment for converting browsers to buyers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (7) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
