BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 70.08000000000001 600 Td (Chapter 12: Getting Your First Reviews) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Reviews are critical because 90 percent of buyers read them before purchasing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Amazon Vine program lets you give free products to trusted reviewers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Request a Review button in Seller Central sends Amazon-approved review requests.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Include a product insert card thanking customers and encouraging reviews.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Never offer incentives, discounts, or free products in exchange for reviews.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Violating review policies will get your account permanently suspended.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Great products and packaging naturally generate positive reviews over time.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Follow up with buyers who contact customer service to ensure satisfaction.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Respond professionally to negative reviews showing you care about quality.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Your first ten reviews are the hardest. After that momentum builds naturally.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Products with at least 15 reviews convert significantly better than those without.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Focus on product quality and customer experience as your review strategy.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 211.2 30 Td (12) Tj ET

